data.description: SPACIOUS, SPACIOUS, SPACIOUS!  This home boasts almost 5,000 sq ft of finished Living Space with 4BR, 3BA and centered on two lots (1.56 acres) and adjacent to an 8 acre Pond with incredible views.  Dramatic Entry.  2x6 Walls, Cherry Cabinets in Kitchen along with brand new Stainless Appliances, Breakfast Nook.  8' Pantry, 6 Panel Doors throughout.  Family Room with Fireplace.  9' Ceilings on Main Floor.  Brand new carpet throughout!  Formal Living and Dining Rooms.  All 4 Bedrooms on upper level. Lower level Rec Room with Pool Table.  Central Vacuum.  3 Car Attached Garage.  Covered concrete Pavilion/Shed in Backyard near Pond.  Lots of new in this well cared for home!  Call today to see this unbelievable home on a spectacular lot!
